6
00:01:13,454 --> 00:01:17,982
I've drunk vodka with russian generals,
black and tans with british battalion troops...

7
00:01:18,022 --> 00:01:19,760
stop talking.

8
00:01:19,800 --> 00:01:21,728
Start drinking.

9
