Come on, let's get you into bed.

19
00:02:30,474 --> 00:02:32,148
Deep breaths...

20
00:02:32,182 --> 00:02:34,743
fresh air. The world is not spinning.

21
00:02:34,793 --> 00:02:36,869
Hey, wait up.

22
00:02:38,710 --> 00:02:41,354
Shouldn't you be in pink
elephant land right about now?

23
00:02:41,387 --> 00:02:43,333
I got another game for you.

24
00:02:43,384 --> 00:02:45,944
Only this time, we both win.

25
00:02:46,229 --> 00:02:48,505
Come on, give me some.

26
00:02:48,605 --> 00:02:52,108
I've got a game for you, football.
It's called hide-and-go seek.

27
00:02:52,175 --> 00:02:54,769
You go hide, and I'll count to a billion.

28
00:02:54,819 --> 00:02:56,945
Ready, set, go.

29
00:02:58,250 --> 00:03:00,525
Aw, come on!
Don't be like that!

30
00:03:00,558 --> 00:03:03,286
You got a girlfriend,
bonehead. Go bug her.

31
00:03:03,336 --> 00:03:04,491
Come on!

32
00:03:08,246 --> 00:03:11,526
Now, don't you think hide-and-seek
would've been a little more fun?

33
00:03:11,626 --> 00:03:13,518
That hurt.

34
00:03:15,529 --> 00:03:18,405
Night-night, party boy.

35
00:03:35,560 --> 00:03:37,808
Go away.

36
00:03:37,887 --> 00:03:40,005
Please, god...

37
00:03:47,186 --> 00:03:51,789
Whoever is pounding on a dorm room door
at 7:00 in the morning...

38
00:03:51,867 --> 00:03:53,593
lois lane?

39
00:03:53,672 --> 00:03:55,241
Do you mind not talking so loud?

40
00:03:55,319 --> 00:03:57,725
There's been a report that you had
an altercation last night with dave cooper.

41
00:03:57,803 --> 00:04:02,335
If "altercation" is defined as "jock attacks,
and I knock the wind out of him," yeah, I confess.

42
00:04:02,413 --> 00:04:05,656
