520
00:39:12,186 --> 00:39:13,943
if you want, I guess you could stay with us.

521
00:39:14,010 --> 00:39:17,608
You're a lifesaver.
God. Am I in need of a hot shower.

522
00:39:18,545 --> 00:39:22,200
Don't worry, smallville.
I'll try to keep it under a half-hour.

523
00:39:26,200 --> 00:39:27,639
What just happened?

524
00:39:41,311 --> 00:39:42,618
Hey!

525
00:39:42,818 --> 00:39:46,015
Looks like you've got a carpool buddy
for weekenders back to smallville.

526
00:39:46,049 --> 00:39:47,488
You got into met U.?

527
00:39:47,538 --> 00:39:50,601
The financial guy said that it's pretty much a lock.
Can you believe it?

528
00:39:50,651 --> 00:39:52,346
Now I don't actually have to rob banks.

529
00:39:52,397 --> 00:39:54,606
Oh, chloe, congratulations.
You deserve it.

530
00:39:54,656 --> 00:39:58,706
