that once you're everybody's all-american,

531
00:39:58,773 --> 00:40:01,707
you will still remember
your old high school buddy.

532
00:40:01,740 --> 00:40:04,401
I mean, you'll still say hi
to me on campus and stuff.

533
00:40:04,468 --> 00:40:06,778
Yeah, um, well, I'm not going to met U.

534
00:40:06,828 --> 00:40:07,971
What?

535
00:40:08,724 --> 00:40:12,573
