and give you the keys to the kingdom?

536
00:40:12,624 --> 00:40:16,512
I'm not playing football anymore.
I turned down my scholarship.

537
00:40:18,376 --> 00:40:22,751
Let me get this straight. You were offered a full ride
with chrome wheels to play the game that you love,

538
00:40:22,818 --> 00:40:26,165
